Keep our January team in your prayers as they connect, learn, transform and respond to the needs of those God puts in front of them. <a href="http://reiserreliefjournal.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">You can follow them on our blog.</a>

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

Our 8th annual Keep the Wheel Turning event will be on Wednesday, April 23, 2014. If you would like to help plan this event, donate auction items, or volunteer at the event please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@reiserrelief.org">info@reiserrelief.org</a>.  You may also learn more by visiting our <a title="Events" href="http://reiserrelief.org/events/">Events</a> page. Together, we can carry on Fr. Reiser’s legacy of love in Haiti.

Read a news story about the event on <a href="%20http://sailor.mnsun.com/2014/04/11/former-plymouth-reverends-ministry-work-carries-on/">Sun Sailor</a> and <a href="http://current.mnsun.com/2014/04/organization-brings-buckets-of-hope-to-haiti/">Sun Current</a>!

